<h1>Aqua Planet</h1>
<p>Aqua Planet is another nice attraction for families. Kids will enjoy the circus show on water, and have a chance to interact with some fish and marine animals. The giant sting ray is an amazing specimen, with a really friendly-looking smile. But perhaps most impressive about Aqua Planet is the location and amazing picturesque view just outside the food court. A great spot to take photos of the ocean and a crater in the background.</p>
